11:Tf70,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What budget do I need to get started?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Most clients invest $2,500 to $15,000 per month in management plus ad spend. We tailor scope to your goals and provide clear pricing after a strategy call."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How quickly will I see results?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Paid media produces data within days and meaningful optimization within 2 to 4 weeks. ROAS typically improves significantly by month 2 or 3 as we refine targeting and creative."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you require long-term contracts?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. We work month to month because results should earn retention, not contract lock-in."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do you report performance?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Weekly optimization notes and monthly dashboards covering spend, ROAS, CPL, conversion rate, and revenue attribution where tracking allows."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How much should I spend on Meta Ads?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"We recommend $3,000 to $15,000 per month in ad spend for most B2B and e-commerce accounts. Management fees start at $1,500 per month on top of ad spend."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you create ad creative for Meta campaigns?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We write ad copy and coordinate image and video creative as part of management. Full video production goes through our video marketing service."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which ad platforms do you manage?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Google Ads, Meta, LinkedIn, and Microsoft Ads. We recommend the mix based on where your buyers actually convert, not platform hype."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you set up conversion tracking?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. GA4, GTM, call tracking, and offline conversion import are standard in week one. We do not optimize blind."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you work with our in-house team?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We collaborate with internal marketers, other agencies, and fractional leaders. We can lead the program or fill a specific channel gap."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What industries do you serve?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Home services, healthcare, professional services, SaaS, e-commerce, and manufacturing. If your buyers search before they buy, we can usually help."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Cuánto debería invertir en Meta Ads?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Recomendamos $3,000 a $15,000 al mes en ad spend para la mayoría de cuentas B2B y e-commerce. Por debajo de $3,000, el algoritmo no tiene datos suficientes para optimizar bien. Las tarifas de gestión parten en $1,500 al mes además del ad spend."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Crean creativos de anuncio para campañas Meta?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Sí. Escribimos copy y coordinamos creativos de imagen y video como parte del programa de gestión. Si necesitas producción de video completa, nuestro servicio de video marketing lo cubre por separado."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿En qué se diferencia la gestión Meta Ads de la gestión PPC?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"PPC Management cubre Google Search, Shopping y Performance Max bajo una tarifa de gestión. Meta Ads es dedicado a Facebook e Instagram con pruebas creativas, audiencias y catalog ads específicos de Meta."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"¿Cuánto tarda Meta Ads en volverse rentable?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Espera 2 a 4 semanas de pruebas creativas antes de encontrar combinaciones ganadoras de anuncio y audiencia. ROAS estable normalmente llega entre las semanas 4 y 8 según tu oferta, volumen creativo y nivel de gasto mensual."}}]}6:[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/#organization\",\"name\":\"KINEXIS Digital\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/assets/logos/KINEXIS_icon_logo.webp\",\"width\":512,\"height\":512},\"description\":\"Digital marketing agency specializing in SEO, paid media, web design, CRO, and analytics for local businesses, SaaS companies, and enterprise organizations.\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/kinexisdigital\"],\"contactPoint\":{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"sales\",\"email\":\"hello@kinexisdigital.com\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"English\",\"Spanish\"]}}"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/es/services/meta-ads#service\",\"name\":\"Meta Ads Management\",\"description\":\"Gestión Meta Ads para Facebook e Instagram. Prospección, retargeting y pruebas creativas construidas para ROAS. Gestión desde $1,500/mes más ad spend.\",\"provider\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/#organization\"},\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/es/services/meta-ads\",\"areaServed\":{\"@type\":\"Country\",\"name\":\"Worldwide\"}}"}}],["$","script","2",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$11"}}],"$L12"],"$L13","$L14"]
